---
title: BeaconLink Session State Machine
---

stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    %% =====================================================
    %% Session Creation
    %% =====================================================

    [*] --> New

    New : Connection Requested
    New : Session ID Pending

    New --> Initializing

    Initializing : Allocate Session Context
    Initializing : Initialize Cryptographic State
    Initializing : Configure Timeouts
    Initializing : Load Trust Configuration

    Initializing --> Authenticating

    %% =====================================================
    %% Authentication Phase
    %% =====================================================

    Authenticating : Mutual TLS Handshake
    Authenticating : Certificate Validation
    Authenticating : Identity Verification

    Authenticating --> Authorizing : Identity Verified
    Authenticating --> AuthenticationFailed : Validation Failed

    AuthenticationFailed : Reject Session
    AuthenticationFailed : Log Security Event

    AuthenticationFailed --> Closed

    Authorizing : Evaluate Session Policies
    Authorizing : Validate Agent Permissions
    Authorizing : Verify Site Authorization

    Authorizing --> Establishing : Authorized
    Authorizing --> AuthorizationFailed : Access Denied

    AuthorizationFailed : Policy Denied
    AuthorizationFailed : Audit Access Failure

    AuthorizationFailed --> Closed

    %% =====================================================
    %% Session Establishment
    %% =====================================================

    Establishing : Create Secure Session
    Establishing : Exchange Session Metadata
    Establishing : Register Session

    Establishing --> Active

    %% =====================================================
    %% Active Session Lifecycle
    %% =====================================================

    state Active {

        [*] --> Idle

        Idle : Await Messages
        Idle : Await Heartbeats
        Idle : Session Active

        Idle --> Receiving : Incoming Message
        Idle --> Sending : Outgoing Message
        Idle --> Synchronizing : State Update
        Idle --> Monitoring : Heartbeat Interval
        Idle --> Renewing : Certificate Renewal
        Idle --> Draining : Graceful Shutdown

        %% -------------------------------------------------
        %% Message Processing
        %% -------------------------------------------------

        Receiving : Receive Secure Message
        Receiving : Verify Integrity
        Receiving : Validate Sequence

        Receiving --> Processing

        Processing : Route Message
        Processing : Apply Policies
        Processing : Update Metrics

        Processing --> Idle

        Sending : Encrypt Payload
        Sending : Sign Message
        Sending : Transmit Message

        Sending --> Idle

        %% -------------------------------------------------
        %% Synchronization
        %% -------------------------------------------------

        Synchronizing : Refresh Desired State
        Synchronizing : Refresh Session Metadata

        Synchronizing --> Idle

        %% -------------------------------------------------
        %% Health Monitoring
        %% -------------------------------------------------

        Monitoring : Verify Heartbeats
        Monitoring : Check Latency
        Monitoring : Validate Session Health

        Monitoring --> Idle : Healthy
        Monitoring --> Degraded : Performance Warning
        Monitoring --> Expired : Heartbeat Timeout

        %% -------------------------------------------------
        %% Certificate Lifecycle
        %% -------------------------------------------------

        Renewing : Refresh Certificates
        Renewing : Re-establish Trust

        Renewing --> Idle : Renewal Successful
        Renewing --> Reauthenticating : Full Revalidation Required

        Reauthenticating : Repeat Identity Validation

        Reauthenticating --> Idle : Successful
        Reauthenticating --> Expired : Validation Failed

        %% -------------------------------------------------
        %% Degraded Operation
        %% -------------------------------------------------

        Degraded : Increased Latency
        Degraded : Reduced Throughput

        Degraded --> Idle : Recovered
        Degraded --> Expired : Connection Lost

        %% -------------------------------------------------
        %% Graceful Drain
        %% -------------------------------------------------

        Draining : Reject New Requests
        Draining : Complete Active Operations

        Draining --> Closing

    }

    %% =====================================================
    %% Session Expiration
    %% =====================================================

    Expired : Session Timeout
    Expired : Identity Invalid
    Expired : Connection Lost

    Expired --> Closing

    %% =====================================================
    %% Session Closure
    %% =====================================================

    Closing : Flush Pending Messages
    Closing : Release Session Resources
    Closing : Remove Routing Entries
    Closing : Publish Disconnect Event

    Closing --> Closed

    Closed : Session Terminated
    Closed : Audit Complete

    Closed --> [*]

    %% =====================================================
    %% Global Failure Paths
    %% =====================================================

    Active --> Closing : Remote Disconnect
    Active --> Closing : Local Disconnect
    Active --> Closing : Administrative Termination
    Initializing --> Closed : Initialization Failure
    Establishing --> Closed : Session Creation Failure